snippet.textDisplay: I love this song. Call me a space-hippy if you must, but when I first opened up the Galaxy Map, I felt many emotions: Immense freedom, a yearning to explore the unknown, the beauty of the galaxy, out relative insignificance, and even a slight twinge of fear that humanity may never reach this level of civilization... All this is wrapped up for me in this song. Beautiful.
